:SPACE:
by Juha Kekäläinen

Sound and music by cone3d/seablue:
http://cone3d.gamedev.net/cgi-bin/index.pl
http://cone3d.gamedev.net/cgi-bin/index.pl?page=tutorials/gfxsdl/tut6

Thanks for them.

This little program is released under GPL license, so you can use it as you want, as long you release source too.

To run program:
./space

To compile program:
make

CONTROLS:
UP = UP
DOWN = DOWN
LEFT = LEFT
RIGHT = RIGHT
CTRL = SHOOT
F1 = TOGGLE FULL SCREEN
ESC = QUIT

You'll need SDL libraries: http://www.libsdl.org/index.php

ps. This program should work on any OS with SDL, just compile and run. This release is compiled for GNU/Linux.
